thread.title_full: Freeze Pro Shop reviewed by ClaireM

author: ClaireM
title: ClaireM
text: Needed to re glue some G3 touring skins. Freeze Pro one of the few stockists of the G3 glue renew strips. The G3 website led us to believe that there was a choice of sizes, only one size on the site, so have some spare glue srip for patch repairs in future. Price was good, certainly massively cheaper than a new pair of skins. Went for free delivery and they arrived the day before expected so very pleased.
